## We add trend lines with `geom_smooth()`

::: {.tiny-font}



::: {.cell output-location='column'}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(blue_jays) +
  aes(body_mass_g, head_length_mm) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_smooth(
    # smooth using linear model
    method = "lm"
  ) +
  theme_bw()
```

